rows.label: tlk006001_01_msg0001
rows.name:
Welcome! Please to make note Melolo
shrewd saleswoman. Not offer special
rate just because friends with Rex!

rows.label: tlk006001_01_msg0002
rows.name:
Rex! It good to see you!
You always welcome!

rows.label: tlk006001_01_msg0003
rows.name:
Demand for salvaged parts seeming
to change with time. Maybe best to
check back regularly!

rows.label: tlk006001_01_msg0004
rows.name:
Rex always passionate about work.
Melolo like that about you. Wish lazy
son would follow example...

rows.label: tlk006001_01_msg0005
rows.name:
It been while since last saw you, Rex.
Tiwitiwi been turning up lots recently.

rows.label: tlk006001_01_msg0006
rows.name:
It show you how people capable of
growing as individuals. Unlike lazy
son. He not grow at all.

rows.label: tlk006001_01_msg0007
rows.name:
Alst is in time of crisis, but Melolo
surprised to find that lazy son not
even venture foot outside door!

rows.label: tlk006001_01_msg0008
rows.name:
When world finally peaceful again,
would ask Rex to teach son example
of role model!
